dy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/diddy">“吹牛老爹”肖恩·库姆斯</a>受到众多指控后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sting">斯汀</a>透露了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-police">警察乐队</a>《你的每一次呼吸》遗产的看法。</p><p> 1983年，The Police 发行了排行榜冠军单曲《Every Breath You Take》。 1997 年，吹牛老爹在自己发行的专辑《I&#39;ll Be Missing You》中采样了这首歌。现在，迪迪面临<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-charged-with-sex-trafficking-racketeering-and-transporting-for-prostitution-3794598">性交易、敲诈勒索和运送卖淫的指控</a>，斯汀分享了他对这位名誉扫地的说唱歌手样本的看法。 </p><figure id="attachment_3796021" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3796021" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3796021" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3796021" class="wp-caption-text">斯汀现场表演。图片来源：Jeremychanphotography/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在接受《 <a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/music/story/2024-11-11/sting-trio-tour-the-police-billy-joel-paul-simon-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>洛杉矶时报》</em></a>最新采访时，当被问及他是否认为警方的袭击事件受到了迪迪封面的污染时，斯汀回答道：“不。我的意思是，我不知道[和迪迪]发生了什么事。但这对我来说根本没有玷污这首歌。这仍然是我的歌。”</p><p>去年，吹牛老爹表示，他被迫在余生中每天向斯汀支付 4,020 英镑（5,000 美元）的样品费。不过，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-says-he-was-joking-about-being-forced-to-pay-sting-5000-a-day-for-the-rest-of-his-life-3427451">很快就收回了这一言论</a>，称自己“在开玩笑！”这才叫搞笑啊！我和@OfficialSting 已经是很久的朋友了！他从来没有因为《想念你》而向我收取每天 3,000 美元或 5,000 美元的费用。他可能每天从历史上最伟大的歌曲之一中赚到超过 5000 美元。”</p><p> Diddy于9月份首次被捕，并被指控犯有性贩运、运送卖淫等罪名。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-denied-bail-in-sex-trafficking-racketeering-case-3794666">他在提供 5000 万美元（3840 万英镑）保释金后被拒绝保释</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/p-diddy-reportedly-placed-on-suicide-watch-while-awaiting-trial-for-sex-crimes-3795772">据报道在等待审判期间他被置于自杀监视之下</a>。此后，该艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-appeals-bail-promises-no-women-and-drug-testing-3798498">对保释被拒绝提出上诉</a>。他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddys-sex-trafficking-trial-date-set-for-2025-3801704">审判日期定于 2025 年 5 月 5 日</a>。</p><p>他仍被联邦拘留在纽约市布鲁克林大都会拘留中心。库姆斯预计将于 12 月 18 日出庭。据<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/sean-diddy-combs-sex-abuse-trial-date-1235129736/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>报道，如果罪名成立，他可能面临最高 15 年的监禁。 </p><figure id="attachment_3807467" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3807467" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3807467" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit.jpg" alt="肖恩·“老爹”库姆斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption 